name: Polygon BabyDoge
description: PolyBabyDoge has learned a few tricks and lessons from his brother BabyDoge and his father Doge. His holders benefit through static rewards and also through the automatic Buy-Back process built into the contract. Together, we are building strong ecosystem including dencentralized exchange (DEX), NFT market and BSC-Polygon cross-chain bridge. Transaction Fee BreakDown: 2% REWARDS TO HOLDERS, 3% DEVELOPMENT TAX, 6% BUYBACK TAX
